overview: Priyathama Neevachata Kusalama (Telugu: ప్రియతమా నీవచట కుశలమా, English: Darling, are you fine there) is a 2013 Telugu film directed by Trinadha Rao Nakkina starring Varun Sandesh, and Komal Jha in the Lead Roles. J. Samba Siva Rao produced this film and Sai Karthik provided the music.
title: Priyathama Neevachata Kushalama
